went through the victim's shin,

05:59.693 --> 06:02.486
the right part of his shin,
and came out through the back of his calf.

06:02.571 --> 06:06.323
Was the dog held at all
for any period of time by the police?

06:06.408 --> 06:08.242
No, it wasn't. No.

06:08.326 --> 06:13.414
Um, in Michigan, law basically states
that people can commit crimes,

06:13.498 --> 06:17.710
that animals aren't some form of, uh,

06:17.794 --> 06:19.295
