I really wouldn't be able to tell you that.

06:30.724 --> 06:33.642
The dog was cute dressed up as a hunter.
There's no doubt about it.

06:33.727 --> 06:35.978
I mean, it was – it was a funny picture,

06:36.063 --> 06:38.439
um, uh, you know, to look at.

06:38.523 --> 06:39.857
It was kind of neat.

06:41.985 --> 06:45.696
Yep, this was the kind of place I was from.

06:45.781 --> 06:48.032
