09:55.387 --> 09:56.637
-12-gauge.
-12-gauge at home?

09:56.721 --> 09:57.930
-Yep.
-Mm-hmm. How about you?

09:58.014 --> 09:59.473
-M16.
-At home?

09:59.557 --> 10:01.600
-Yep.
-Yeah?

10:01.685 --> 10:02.977
