10:07.357 --> 10:09.483
I know where they're gonna go
when I aim and shoot.

10:09.567 --> 10:11.902
Whose idea was the calendar?

10:11.987 --> 10:14.905
-That would probably be Kristen.
-A picture's worth a thousand words.

10:14.990 --> 10:18.701
I mean, it's not – A, it demonstrates
a level of sophistication

10:18.785 --> 10:21.370
that you wouldn't expect out of militia.

10:21.454 --> 10:24.415
B, you know, we're people too.

10:24.499 --> 10:26.625
-Right.
