10:26.710 --> 10:31.547
It was a fund-raiser,
and it showed that we're not so serious.

10:31.631 --> 10:35.467
You know, we're not these conspiracy nuts
who wouldn't want our pictures to get out.

10:35.552 --> 10:40.014
And it was a fun fund-raiser, you know?

10:40.098 --> 10:43.142
I've had guns, um,

10:43.226 --> 10:46.103
pretty much since I was old enough
to have them.

10:46.187 --> 10:48.689
