11:01.036 --> 11:04.747
When a criminal breaks into your house,
who's the first person you're gonna call?

11:04.831 --> 11:07.958
Most people will call the police
because they have guns.

11:09.169 --> 11:11.045
Cut out the middleman. Take care of it.

11:11.129 --> 11:14.006
- Take care of your own family yourself.

11:14.090 --> 11:18.093
If you're not going to
protect your family, who is?

11:18.178 --> 11:20.637
We're not racists.
We're not extremists.

11:20.722 --> 11:22.264
We're not fundamentalists.

11:22.349 --> 11:25.517
We're not terrorists or militants
or other such nonsense.

11:25.602 --> 11:28.103
-We're citizens.
-We're just concerned citizens.

11:28.188 --> 11:32.358
We have a desire to fulfill our responsibilities
and duties as Americans,

11:32.442 --> 11:34.443
