12:06.768 --> 12:10.604
This is James Nichols,
the brother of Terry Nichols.

12:10.688 --> 12:13.232
James graduated from high school
the same year I did

12:13.316 --> 12:15.025
in the district next to mine.

12:15.735 --> 12:17.778
On this farm in Decker, Michigan,

12:17.862 --> 12:21.365
McVeigh and the Nichols brothers
made practice bombs before Oklahoma City.

12:22.742 --> 12:26.286
Terry and James were both arrested
in connection to the bombing.

12:26.371 --> 12:29.540
US attorneys formally linked
the Nichols brothers of Michigan

12:29.624 --> 12:32.376
with Oklahoma bomb suspect
Timothy McVeigh.

12:32.460 --> 12:34.253
Officials charged James,
who was at the hearing,

12:34.337 --> 12:36.255
and Terry, who was not,

12:36.339 --> 12:39.758
with conspiring to make
and possess small bombs.

12:39.843 --> 12:42.928
Terry Nichols was convicted
and received a life sentence.

12:43.012 --> 12:46.098
Timothy McVeigh was executed.

12:46.182 --> 12:50.310
But the feds didn't have the goods on James,
so the charges were dropped.

12:50.395 --> 12:54.940
I'm just glad to be out and free
so I can get on with my life.

12:55.024 --> 12:57.943
-Did Timothy McVeigh ever stay here?
-Yes. Yes.

12:58.027 --> 12:59.903
He stayed here several times.

12:59.988 --> 13:02.948
For the longest period,
about three months or so. I don't know.

13:03.032 --> 13:04.450
But he was a nice guy.

13:04.534 --> 13:06.034
- Decent guy.
- Yeah.

13:06.119 --> 13:08.954
- They didn't find anything on this farm?
- As to what?

13:09.038 --> 13:11.165
-Bomb-making material?
-Any kind of explosives.

13:11.249 --> 13:14.585
Yeah, I had blasting caps,
dynamite blasting caps,

13:14.669 --> 13:18.881
dynamite fuse, black powder –
you know, for muzzle loaders.

13:18.965 --> 13:21.008
Sure. Diesel fuel, fertilizer.

13:21.092 --> 13:23.218
But that is normal farm stuff.

13:23.303 --> 13:25.888
That is no way connected
in any way whatsoever

13:25.972 --> 13:28.891
to the Oklahoma City bombing
or bomb-making.

13:28.975 --> 13:33.520
Them people, law enforcement,
if you want to call them that, were here,

13:33.605 --> 13:36.315
and they were shaking in their shoes.

13:36.399 --> 13:39.735
They were physically shaking.
Scared to death.

13:39.819 --> 13:40.944
Of?

13:41.029 --> 13:43.739
Because they thought
this was gonna be another Waco.

13:43.823 --> 13:45.532
Because certain people,

13:47.452 --> 13:50.037
namely my ex-wife and other people,

13:50.914 --> 13:53.165
said I'm a radical, I'm a wild man,

13:53.249 --> 13:55.959
I got a gun under every arm,
down every leg,

13:56.044 --> 13:58.462
in every shoe, every corner of the house.

13:58.546 --> 14:01.256
You say anything to me, I'll shoot you.

14:01.341 --> 14:04.426
If the people find out
how they've been ripped off

14:04.511 --> 14:09.932
and – and enslaved in this country
by the government,

14:10.016 --> 14:11.850
by the powers to be...

14:14.687 --> 14:18.440
they will revolt with anger,

14:19.275 --> 14:21.276
with merciless anger.

14:21.361 --> 14:23.278
There'll be blood running in the streets.

14:23.363 --> 14:28.450
