14:39.379 --> 14:43.674
Oscoda has a bad habit of raising psychos.
Bad habit of it.

14:43.758 --> 14:45.133
This is Brent.

14:45.218 --> 14:47.427
And this is his buddy, D.J.

14:47.512 --> 14:52.391
They live in Oscoda, Michigan,
across the bay from the Nichols' farm.

14:52.475 --> 14:55.102
Eric Harris, who would later
go on to commit the massacre

14:55.186 --> 14:57.688
at Columbine High School in Colorado,

14:57.772 --> 14:59.856
spent part of his childhood here.

15:01.067 --> 15:03.569
Eric lived on the air force base in Oscoda,

15:03.653 --> 15:06.989
where his dad flew planes
during the Gulf War.

15:07.824 --> 15:09.783
Twenty percent of all the bombs
dropped in that war

15:09.867 --> 15:12.995
were from planes
that took off from Oscoda.

15:14.080 --> 15:16.957
I asked Brent if he remembered
anything about Eric.

15:17.041 --> 15:20.627
I never knew him, but I knew of him.
He left here before I got here.

15:20.712 --> 15:22.713
I've only lived here
about seven years, off and on.

15:22.797 --> 15:25.674
He's about the same age as you,
so you must have people in your class that –

15:25.758 --> 15:28.844
Yeah, like a friend of mine.
He knows him. He was in class with him.

15:28.928 --> 15:30.470
He's lived up here all of his life.

15:30.555 --> 15:34.141
I went to school with him,
and it shocked me to hear it on the news.

15:34.225 --> 15:39.146
You know, that especially a kid from here
would be doing that.

15:39.230 --> 15:42.774
I didn't last too long in this high school here.
I got kicked out. I got expelled.

15:42.859 --> 15:45.569
-Why was that?
-I had a run-in with a kid one time.

15:45.653 --> 15:48.030
And I pulled a weapon on him –
pulled a gun on him.

15:48.114 --> 15:50.240
-A gun? What kind of gun?
-Nine millimeter.

15:50.325 --> 15:52.576
I could've made a mess out of that situation.

15:52.660 --> 15:53.994
- Could've been worse.
- A lot worse.

15:54.078 --> 15:56.413
-You could've been Eric Harris.
-I could've been.

15:56.497 --> 15:59.958
-So they kicked you out of school?
-They kicked me out for 380 days.

16:00.043 --> 16:03.086
Or 165 days.
Whatever a full school year is.

16:03.963 --> 16:07.549
Matter of fact, for the longest time that's
what my plan was – to move out to Colorado.

16:07.634 --> 16:09.134
Colorado?

16:09.218 --> 16:11.345
