that kind of predatory action,

23:46.509 --> 23:49.010
that kind of indiscriminate,

23:49.095 --> 23:51.429
um, killing.

23:56.310 --> 23:59.312
This facility where we're located right now

23:59.396 --> 24:03.066
and two other major facilities
where our employees work

24:03.150 --> 24:06.194
are either in or very near Littleton.

24:06.278 --> 24:10.115
So we have over 5,000 employees
at these facilities,

24:10.199 --> 24:12.700
quite a number of whom live in Littleton,

24:12.785 --> 24:15.328
many of whom have children
who attend Columbine High School.

24:15.412 --> 24:18.915
I suppose in one way you could say
that what happened at Columbine High School

24:18.999 --> 24:23.920
is a microcosm, uh,
of what happens throughout the world.

24:24.672 --> 24:28.258
You know the signs we see around here,
