24:33.305 --> 24:34.806
you're the biggest weapons-maker.

24:34.890 --> 24:36.349
"We are Columbine"?

24:36.433 --> 24:38.726
I think we probably embody that spirit

24:38.811 --> 24:40.770
that, yeah, we're all members
