24:40.855 --> 24:45.275
and it behooves us to help one another
and to reach out to assist one another.

24:45.359 --> 24:50.238
He told us that no one in Littleton,
including the executives at Lockheed,

24:50.322 --> 24:54.117
could figure out why the boys at Columbine
had resorted to violence.

24:54.201 --> 24:56.744
Why – Why would kids do this?

24:56.829 --> 24:59.747
Some of the root of that

24:59.832 --> 25:04.043
probably has to do
with their anger about various issues.

25:04.128 --> 25:08.464
And we became aware of a program
that provides anger management training.

25:08.549 --> 25:13.303
So we made a $100,000 contribution
to the Jefferson County Schools

25:13.387 --> 25:15.680
to use this training in the schools.

25:15.764 --> 25:19.392
We hope to help both teachers and students

25:19.476 --> 25:23.104
learn alternative ways to deal with anger.

25:23.189 --> 25:25.523
