This is Dick Clark's
American Bandstand Grill,

01:35:14.584 --> 01:35:17.586
where Tamarla worked one of her two jobs.

01:35:17.670 --> 01:35:18.837
♪ Bandstand ♪

01:35:18.922 --> 01:35:22.466
She was a –
She worked in this room as a bartender,

01:35:22.550 --> 01:35:27.137
a fountain person making drinks,
making shakes, desserts.

01:35:27.222 --> 01:35:29.181
-Was she a good employee?
-Yeah, she was.

01:35:29.265 --> 01:35:32.309
She also worked at the Fudgery
in the mall here.

01:35:32.394 --> 01:35:34.978
Right, where the state had placed her.

01:35:35.063 --> 01:35:37.564
Dick Clark is an American icon.

01:35:37.649 --> 01:35:40.067
The man who brought rock and roll
into our homes

01:35:40.151 --> 01:35:42.361
every week on American Bandstand.

01:35:42.445 --> 01:35:45.531
Every part of your life you can link up
to a part of music usually.

01:35:45.615 --> 01:35:48.575
So, as Dick says,
it's the soundtrack of our lives.

01:35:48.660 --> 01:35:50.786
Music is the soundtrack of our lives.

01:35:50.870 --> 01:35:53.831
His restaurant
and the Fudgery here in Auburn Hills

01:35:53.915 --> 01:35:58.794
applied for special tax breaks because
they were using welfare people as employees.

01:35:59.838 --> 01:36:04.341
Even though Tamarla worked up to 70 hours
a week at these two jobs in the mall,

01:36:04.426 --> 01:36:06.760
she did not earn enough to pay her rent,

01:36:06.845 --> 01:36:09.555
and one week before the shooting

01:36:09.639 --> 01:36:12.641
was told by her landlord
that he was evicting her.

01:36:13.643 --> 01:36:17.646
With nowhere to go and not wanting
to take her two children out of school,

01:36:17.730 --> 01:36:21.358
Tamarla asked her brother
if they could stay with him for a few weeks.

01:36:22.193 --> 01:36:26.196
It was there that Tamarla's son
found a small .32-caliber gun

01:36:26.281 --> 01:36:28.365
and took it to school.

01:36:28.450 --> 01:36:31.160
Tamarla did not see him
take the gun to school

01:36:31.244 --> 01:36:34.329
because she was on a state bus
to go serve drinks

01:36:34.414 --> 01:36:36.290
and make fudge for rich people.

01:36:36.374 --> 01:36:40.377
